                  <div><dt>MODEL</dt><dd>BM25 + vector cosine + rerank + time weighting</dd></div>
                  <div><dt>WHY</dt><dd>Balances lexical precision with semantic continuity</dd></div>
                  <div class="risk-row"><dt>RISK</dt><dd>Stale memory overweighting or recency bias under stress</dd></div>
                  <div class="gate-row"><dt>GATE</dt><dd>Score breakdown inspection + freshness weight + validation packet check</dd></div>
                </dl>
              </article>
