        <section class="exec eq-walk" aria-label="Operational walkthrough for pipeline state evolution">
          <p class="kicker">Operational Walkthrough: Pipeline State Evolution (Detect → Decode → Render → Enhance)</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Detect (T):</strong> capture source intent and runtime context from `uterm`, `quantum-notepad`, and commander input channels.</li>
            <li><strong>Decode (D):</strong> classify/parse lines into structural coordinates via prefix + DAC paths before any export or dispatch.</li>
            <li><strong>Render (R):</strong> materialize UI/state outputs (cards, traces, charts, terminal output) for operator review.</li>
            <li><strong>Enhance (E):</strong> reinject retrieval-memory and confidence feedback to improve the next operator cycle.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
