            <li><strong>Confidence gate:</strong> when probability falls below τ, payload escalates to tensor context (`TensorHead`) instead of forcing bad labels.</li>
            <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> low-confidence noise is isolated and corrected without slowing high-confidence paths.</li>
            <li><strong>Product effect:</strong> fewer silent misroutes in automation and safer autonomous patch generation.</li>
