                <div class="meta"><div class="meta-top"><b>E11 — Unified Cycle Operator Π</b><span class="status-chip validated">Validated</span></div><span>Composed operator blocks and stage dependencies</span></div>
              </article>
              <article class="eq-matrix-card controls">
                <div class="meta"><div class="meta-top"><b>Chart Pack Controls</b><span class="status-chip published">Live</span></div><span>Switch all matrix cards between Default, Bloch, 3D Cube, and Circuit views.</span></div>
                <div class="eq-matrix-options inline" aria-label="Chart options">
                  <button type="button" class="eq-matrix-opt is-active" data-chart-pack="default">Default</button>
                  <button type="button" class="eq-matrix-opt" data-chart-pack="bloch">Bloch</button>
                  <button type="button" class="eq-matrix-opt" data-chart-pack="cube">3D Cube</button>
                  <button type="button" class="eq-matrix-opt" data-chart-pack="circuit">Circuit</button>
                </div>
              </article>
              <article class="eq-matrix-card controls">
                <div class="meta">
                  <div class="meta-top"><b>E03 Extension Lane</b><span class="status-chip validated">Validated</span></div>
                  <span>Qw composite lane expansion for side-by-side dimension checks below the primary matrix cards.</span>
                  <span style="margin-top:6px;">alpha=.35 · beta=.22 · gamma=.27 · delta=.16 · median Qw=.79</span>
                </div>
