            <li><strong>Gap to submission:</strong> convert this launch paper into manuscript form (Abstract, Intro, Related Work, Methods, Experiments, Results, Limitations).</li>
            <li><strong>Evidence gates:</strong> benchmark protocol, datasets/traces, hardware table, statistical reporting, claim→figure/table map.</li>
