            <li><strong>Weeks 6–10:</strong> draft manuscript + supplement package, complete metadata/policy checks, prepare preprint and journal submission files.</li>
            <li><strong>Weeks 10–12:</strong> submit preprint, start journal submission cycle, and align boardroom narrative to measured deltas.</li>
